# …but allow the GeoLite2 City DB into the build context so deploy/Dockerfile.geoip
# can bake it into a private image (see deploy/GEOIP.md). It only enters the context
# when the file is actually present, and the base Dockerfile never COPYs it, so base
# images stay database-free.
